{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Hey Listen</strong></i><strong>:</strong>\u00a0The demo for this game is the full game. Only purchase if you want to support future games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>WARNING:</strong> This game will destroy friendships.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <i><strong>We Are Square</strong></i> you and up to seven friends must work together to control one square and platform yourselves to the goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316390/extras/updown.png?t=1734754134\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Featuring:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Exactly 1 music track!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 24 levels! (there are 25 levels... and some of them are jokes)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enough tricky platforming to make you hate your friends!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A &quot;Blame Screen&quot; after every death to let you know which of your friends is holding you back!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Designed for local co-op but works with Steam's Remote Play feature</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gamepads are required. Due to coding weirdness, only 4 controllers can be Xbox controllers. For 5+ player gameplay, PlayStation or generic gamepads must be used.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Square Wars","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3316390/b11e29070a16b42c488d4eaaa8a9a71531293dc6.jpg"},{"name":"Revenge Of The Square","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3316390/736d4cff7762e3b53cf3d605282974b813b7f01a.jpg"},{"name":"A New Square","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3316390/b09b13daf0e963d2b2925ff55fa105bb06a88d6d.jpg"},{"name":"The Square Strikes Back","path":"https://cdn.akamai.